@startuml
!theme plain

title [Scenario Name] Flow

' ============================================================================
' Participants
' ============================================================================

actor "User" as User
participant "Web App" as Web
participant "API Server" as API
database "Database" as DB

' Optional external systems:
' participant "External Service" as Ext

' ============================================================================
' Main Flow
' ============================================================================

autonumber

== Initialization ==

User -> Web: Action description
activate Web

Web -> API++: POST /endpoint
API -> DB: Query
activate DB
DB --> API: Result
deactivate DB

' ============================================================================
' Conditional Logic
' ============================================================================

alt Success case
  API --> Web: 200 OK + data
  Web --> User: Show success
else Error case
  API --> Web--: 400/500 Error
  Web --> User: Show error message
  deactivate Web
end

' ============================================================================
' Cleanup / Finalization
' ============================================================================

== Cleanup ==

note over API: Optional cleanup steps
API --> Web--: Final response
Web --> User: Done
deactivate Web

@enduml
